name: Diana Camera Tote Bag
description:
My illustration of the Lomography camera - the Diana Mini, has been screen printed with two colours onto a crisp white cotton tote bag.

It's lightweight enough to fold away and have handy but sturdy enough to carry your things as a bag on it's own. Best thing is it's reusable. Perfect for photographers to carry their camera in!

Materials/Size:

Bag Weighs 5oz
100% Cotton - White
14.9" Width x 16.9" Height with Long handles

All sizes are approximate. Please note the colours on monitors can vary slightly from the actual product but it should be very close. Each bag is unique.

name: Diana Mini Camera - Blank Card
description:
The perfect greetings card to give to a lomography or film user. 

My hand drawn Diana mini Camera illustration has been digitally printed onto the front of this A6 size card. The inside has been left blank for you to add your own personal message. 

Card comes with a crisp white envelope and as the front of the card is free from any text it would look great in a frame after it's use. 

A6 card - 4.13" x 5.82" (105mm x 148mm) 

Actual card is of excellent quality thick card stock.

Please note the colours on different monitors can vary slightly from the actual print but it should be very close.

name: Diana Mini Camera Keychain
description:
These little keychains are perfect for Lomography fans. My Diana mini camera illustration has been printed onto acrylic to make this cute camera keyring.

The Keyring made of acrylic, the camera charm measures approx 1 inch by 1.5 inches at the longest side and is 3mm thick - perfect size for those keys to fit nicely in your pocket.

Please note the colours on different monitors can vary slightly from the actual item but it should be very close.

name: Polaroid Keychain
description:
My illustration of an old Polaroid camera has been printed onto acrylic and made into this camera keyring!

It fits in your pocket and brightens up your keys, and makes a great gift for any photographer or camera geek.

Materials/size:

This Keyring is made of acrylic, and the polaroid camera charm measures approx 1.5" by 1.2" and is 3mm thick - perfect size for those keys to fit nicely in your pocket.

Please note the colours on different monitors can vary slightly from the actual item but it should be very close.
